            "display_name": "Sandhu Santhakumar"
        },
        "content_license": "CC BY-SA 3.0",
        "score": 1,
        "is_accepted": true,
        "last_activity_date": 1384945185,
        "creation_date": 1384945185,
        "body": "<p>It will use the default version of Java.<\/p>\n\n<p>To change this<\/p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <code>Control Panel &gt; Java &gt; Advanced &gt; Default Java for Browsers<\/code> and uncheck <code>Microsoft Internet Explorer<\/code>.<\/li>\n<li>Go to <code>C:\\Program Files\\Java\\jre_version_you_need_to_use\\bin<\/code>, and run <code>javacpl.exe<\/code>. Go to <code>Advanced &gt; Default Java for Browsers<\/code> and check <code>Microsoft Internet Explorer<\/code>.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "answer_id": 20094066,
        "question_id": 20093931
    }],
